<exercise id="fs-id1172096195012">
<problem id="fs-id1172098276715">
<para id="fs-id1172100638174">Algae with chloroplasts with three or four membranes are a result of ________ ________.</para>
</problem>
<solution id="fs-id1172098381989">
<para id="fs-id1172098310905">secondary endosymbiosis</para>
</solution>
